    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"layout":"doc.js","slug":"docs/api/spi","title":"SPI"},"html":"<h1 id=\"spi\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spi\" aria-label=\"spi permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SPI</h1>\n<p>The <code class=\"language-text\">spi</code> module supports communication with devices using SPI (Serial Peripheral Interface) bus as the master device. Use <code class=\"language-text\">require('spi')</code> to access this module. A chip select pin of slave device need to be controlled by GPIO output pin.</p>\n<h2 id=\"class-spi\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#class-spi\" aria-label=\"class spi permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Class: SPI</h2>\n<p>An instances of <code class=\"language-text\">SPI</code> represents a SPI bus.</p>\n<h3 id=\"spimode_0\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spimode_0\" aria-label=\"spimode_0 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SPI.MODE_0</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">0</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>'SPI MODE0: CPOL = 0, CPHA = 0</p>\n<h3 id=\"spimode_1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spimode_1\" aria-label=\"spimode_1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SPI.MODE_1</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">1</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>'SPI MODE0: CPOL = 0, CPHA = 1</p>\n<h3 id=\"spimode_2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spimode_2\" aria-label=\"spimode_2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SPI.MODE_2</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">2</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>'SPI MODE0: CPOL = 1, CPHA = 0</p>\n<h3 id=\"spimode_3\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spimode_3\" aria-label=\"spimode_3 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SPI.MODE_3</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">3</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>'SPI MODE0: CPOL = 1, CPHA = 1</p>\n<h3 id=\"spimsb\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spimsb\" aria-label=\"spimsb permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SPI.MSB</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">0</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>SPI bitorder, MSB is the first bit.</p>\n<h3 id=\"spilsb\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spilsb\" aria-label=\"spilsb permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SPI.LSB</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> = <code class=\"language-text\">1</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>SPI bitorder, LSB is the first bit.</p>\n<h3 id=\"new-spibus-options\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#new-spibus-options\" aria-label=\"new spibus options permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>new SPI(bus[, options])</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">bus</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> SPI bus number.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">options</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;object></code> The object of SPI options. <em>Default values are depends on board (Check in a board page).</em>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">mode</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> <code class=\"language-text\">SPI.MODE_0</code> (CPOL=0/CPHA=0), <code class=\"language-text\">SPI.MODE_1</code> (CPOL=0/CPHA=1), <code class=\"language-text\">SPI.MODE_2</code> (CPOL=1/CPHA=0), or <code class=\"language-text\">SPI.MODE_3</code> (CPOL=1/CPHA=1). <strong>Default:</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">SPI.MODE_0</code>.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">baudrate</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Baud rate. <strong>Default:</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">3000000</code>, 3 Mbit/s</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">bitorder</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> <code class=\"language-text\">SPI.MSB (0)</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">SPI.LSB (1)</code> <strong>Default:</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">SPI.MSB (0)</code>.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">sck</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> SPI SCK pin number.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">mosi</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> SPI MOSI (TX) pin number.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">miso</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> SPI MISO (RX) pin number.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Returns:</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;object></code> An initialized SPI instance corresponds to the bus number. Once initialized, the same object will be returned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Instances of the <code class=\"language-text\">SPI</code> class can be created using the new keyword or by calling spi.SPI() as a function. A <code class=\"language-text\">RangeError</code> will be thrown if <strong><code class=\"language-text\">bus</code></strong> is not less than max bus number. Please see <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Serial_Peripheral_Interface#Clock_polarity_and_phase\">here</a> for more about SPI modes.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Create the SPI instance with master mode</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token constant\">GPIO</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'gpio'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token constant\">SPI</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'spi'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> spi0cs <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">GPIO</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token constant\">OUTPUT</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Set chip select to pin 9.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> spiOptions <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// SPI options</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">mode</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">SPI</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">MODE_0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">baudrate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">800000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">bitorder</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">SPI</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">MSB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> spi0 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SPI</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> spiOptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ChipSelect LOW</span>\nspi0cs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">write</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">LOW</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// transfer data...</span>\nspi0<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">close</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Close SPI bus 0</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"spitransferdata-timeout\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#spitransferdata-timeout\" aria-label=\"spitransferdata timeout permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>spi.transfer(data[, timeout])</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">data</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Uint8Array|string></code> Data to write.</li>\n<li><strong><code class=\"language-text\">timeout</code></strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;number></code> Timeout in milliseconds. <strong>Default:</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">5000</code>.</li>\n<li><strong>Returns:</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Uint8Array></code> Received data or <code class=\"language-text\">null</code> if failed to transfer or timeout.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Send and receive data simultaneously via SPI bus.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token constant\">GPIO</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'gpio'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token constant\">SPI</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'spi'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> spi0cs <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">GPIO</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">9</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token constant\">OUTPUT</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Set chip select to pin 9.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> spiOptions <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// SPI options</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">mode</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">SPI</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">MODE_0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">baudrate</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">800000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">bitorder</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">SPI</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">MSB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> spi0 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SPI</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> spiOptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ChipSelect LOW</span>\nspi0cs<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">write</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">LOW</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Send two bytes and receive two bytes</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> buf <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> spi0<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">transfer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Uint8Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0x88</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x24</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// send and receive two byte data.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buf<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// == 2</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// first byte</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// second byte</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"spisenddata-t